w tail, and that the\nmagnitude of returns is highly autocorrelated (also known as clustered\nvolatility).\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 24 Apr 2008 00:22:50 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 8 Jul 2008 19:40:04 GMT"}],"update_date":"2008-12-02"}
